- Global styling: Ensure consistency with LifeOps global styles (dark UI, typography, and color tokens). The component should not clash with existing global styles and should respect CSS-in-JS or CSS module conventions used in the project.
- Accessibility & SEO:
  - Title tag should reflect the policy page (e.g., Privacy Policy – LifeOps).
  - Meta description should summarize the page purpose succinctly.
  - ARIA landmarks for main content and sections.

